Grammaire

    0 $accept: program $end

    1 program: optional_newlines BEGIN_KW NEWLINE listinstr END_KW optional_newlines

    2 optional_newlines: /* vide */
    3                  | optional_newlines NEWLINE

    4 listinstr: listinstr statement
    5          | statement

    6 statement: instr NEWLINE
    7          | NEWLINE
    8          | error NEWLINE

    9 instr: declaration
   10      | affectation
   11      | lecture
   12      | ecriture
   13      | boucle

   14 declaration: INT_KW ID

   15 affectation: ID ASSIGN expr

   16 lecture: READ_KW LPAREN ID RPAREN

   17 ecriture: WRITE_KW expr

   18 boucle: WHILE_KW LPAREN cond RPAREN DO_KW NEWLINE listinstr OD_KW

   19 expr: expr PLUS expr
   20     | expr MINUS expr
   21     | expr MUL expr
   22     | expr DIV expr
   23     | expr MOD expr
   24     | expr POW expr
   25     | MINUS expr
   26     | LPAREN expr RPAREN
   27     | ID
   28     | NUM

   29 cond: expr condsymb expr

   30 condsymb: GT
   31         | LT
   32         | GE
   33         | LE
   34         | EQ
   35         | NE
   36         | STRICT_EQ


